ow function calling works under the hood — and why the interplay between tool use and model reasoning is what makes or breaks agentic systems.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://tulamasterman.com/assets/images/reasoning-toolcalling-blog.png" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://tulamasterman.com/assets/images/reasoning-toolcalling-blog.png" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Navigating the Latest GenAI Model Announcements — July 2024</title><link href="https://tulamasterman.com/writing/navigating-latest-genai-model-announcements/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Navigating the Latest GenAI Model Announcements — July 2024" /><published>2024-07-25T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2024-07-25T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://tulamasterman.com/writing/navigating-latest-genai-model-announcements</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://tulamasterman.com/writing/navigating-latest-genai-model-announcements/"><![CDATA[]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="Navigating a Fast-Moving Field" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[GPT-4o mini, Llama 3.1, Mistral NeMo 12B — July 2024 brought a wave of model releases. Here's a clear-eyed guide to what actually changed, what's worth paying attention to, and what's mostly noise.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://tulamasterman.com/assets/images/july-2024-announcements-blog.png" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://tulamasterman.com/assets/images/july-2024-announcements-blog.png" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Understanding Techniques for Solving GenAI Challenges</title><link href="https://tulamasterman.com/writing/understanding-techniques-for-solving-genai-challenges/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Understanding Techniques for Solving GenAI Challenges" /><published>2024-05-14T00:00:00+00: